{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/research/paper-reading/boundless-socratic-learning/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"mem 的小站"}},"post":{"id":"d91e9e2d-a397-5522-83d6-0438edf0c207","excerpt":"Abstract 作者指出在封闭系统中训练的智能体能够掌握任何期望的能力，只需满足：(a) 获得充分信息量且对其的反馈；(b) 经验/数据覆盖足够广泛；(c) 具有足够的容量与资源。作者讨论了当 (c) 不构成瓶颈时，封闭系统中 (a) 和 (b…","html":"<h2 id=\"anchor-a2157fdb6e649030\" style=\"position: relative;\"><a href=\"#anchor-a2157fdb6e649030\" aria-label=\"anchor a2157fdb6e649030 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Abstract</h2>\n<p>作者指出在封闭系统中训练的智能体能够掌握任何期望的能力，只需满足：(a) 获得充分信息量且对其的反馈；(b) 经验/数据覆盖足够广泛；(c) 具有足够的容量与资源。作者讨论了当 (c) 不构成瓶颈时，封闭系统中 (a) 和 (b) 带来的限制，并提出了一种基于语言游戏概念、纯粹的递归自我改进框架（称为“苏格拉底式学习”），而其局限仅在于时间及逐渐出现的对其偏差。</p>\n<h2 id=\"anchor-4066145df9e2eb0d\" style=\"position: relative;\"><a href=\"#anchor-4066145df9e2eb0d\" aria-label=\"anchor 4066145df9e2eb0d permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Insights</h2>\n<p>考虑一个随时间演变的封闭系统（无输入、无输出）。系统内有一个具有输入和输出的实体，称为智能体，它也会随时间发生变化。系统外部有一个观察者，其目的是评估智能体的性能。如果性能不断提高，我们就把这对系统和观察者称为改进过程。</p>\n<h2 id=\"anchor-2eec55694e7f5fe5\" style=\"position: relative;\"><a href=\"#anchor-2eec55694e7f5fe5\" aria-label=\"anchor 2eec55694e7f5fe5 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>References</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/EC5QdHcasev8JpTp-OKLKQ\">DeepMind 用语言游戏让大模型学 AlphaGo 自我博弈，数据限制不存在了 - (mp.weixin.qq.com)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/aixedu/posts/558272810501777/\">ChatGPT x AI 融入教學 | 一個封閉環境下，人工智慧有沒有可能透過遞廻歸來實現自我改進能力 | Facebook</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-a2157fdb6e649030\">Abstract</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-4066145df9e2eb0d\">Insights</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-2eec55694e7f5fe5\">References</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Boundless Socratic Learning with Language Games","description":null},"fields":{"cover":null,"slug":"/research/paper-reading/boundless-socratic-learning/","cssclasses":null,"isDoc":null,"authors":[],"createTime":"2025 年 4 月 22 日","updateTime":"2025 年 4 月 22 日","category":"[{\"name\":\"科研\",\"to\":\"/research/\"},{\"name\":\"论文精读\",\"to\":\"/research/paper-reading/\"}]","propsJson":null}},"previous":null,"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"d91e9e2d-a397-5522-83d6-0438edf0c207","previousPostId":null,"nextPostId":null,"navJson":""}},"staticQueryHashes":["3871233186"],"slicesMap":{}}